**Refining RLS Implementation**

I've incorporated the RLS policies into the schema definition. I'm focusing on their placement to prevent any permission issues in the app's functionality, as we've discussed before. The tables are now set, including the users, catalog, nota_empenho, products, and movements. I'm taking a last look at the tables to confirm the columns match the code.


